# Korean documentation (local only). Internal planning / review docs
# (ARCHITECTURE.ko.md, EXPERT_REVIEW_*.ko.md, SESSION_*.ko.md) stay
# here and out of the public repo. Public Korean legal notices live
# at ``docs/*.ko.md`` to avoid the parent-directory re-include trap
# (git cannot negate files under an excluded directory).
docs/ko/

# Claude Code / agent local config
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
# …but ship repo-level slash commands so every contributor
# gets `/ploidy` without manual setup.
!.claude/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/*.md

# Template convention: planning TODO is kept local per developer
TODO.md

# Internal notes (local only)
docs/internal/
docs/paper-draft.md

# Experiment local-only scripts
experiments/src/resume_all.sh
experiments/src/skills_fresh_design.py
experiments/EXPERIMENT_SPEC_UNIFIED.md

# Experiment results and logs (large, regenerated locally)
experiments/results/
experiments/logs/
experiments/phase*.log

# LaTeX intermediate artifacts (everywhere)
**/*.aux
**/*.blg
**/*.log
**/*.out
**/*.fls
**/*.fdb_latexmk
**/*.synctex.gz
**/*.toc
**/*.lof
**/*.lot
**/*.nav
**/*.snm
**/*.vrb
**/missfont.log

# Preprint working copies (regenerated); submission snapshots in submissions/ stay tracked
paper/main.pdf
paper/main.bbl

# Debate scratch / review artifacts (generated locally by ploidy debate runs;
# contain synthetic scenarios that reference external personas — keep out of
# the public repo per the portfolio PII rule).
ARCHITECTURE_ANALYSIS_*.md
ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW_*.md
FIVE_REVIEWER_*.md
FOUR_REVIEWER_*.md
MIGRATION_RISK_*.md
CONSOLIDATED_ISSUES_*.md
.consolidated_review_*.md
.neoql_risk_*.md
.tmp_arch_*.md

# Misplaced experiment results (canonical location is experiments/results/)
experiments/src/results/

# The `!.claude/` negation above re-includes the whole agent dir; re-exclude
# the worktree subdirectory so transient agent worktrees stay local.
.claude/worktrees/
